OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 16 Apr to Sat 25 Apr
OL,6,FChangeable at the start of this period
OL,7,Fwith low pressure to the west or
OL,8,Fnorthwest of the UK. This will bring
OL,9,Fshowers or longer spells of rain at
OL,10,Ftimes, heaviest and most persistent in
OL,11,Fthe northwest together with some
OL,12,Fstrong winds. The southeast is likely
OL,13,Fto be driest and brightest. Later in
OL,14,Fthis period, conditions may become
OL,15,Fdrier and more settled, perhaps more
OL,16,Fespecially in the north or northwest
OL,17,Fwith the south possibly becoming the
OL,18,Ffocus for showers or longer spells of
OL,19,Frain. Temperatures will likely be near
OL,20,For slightly above average overall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
